snippet.title: Introducing Bitmoji Party!
snippet.description:
Become your Bitmoji. Challenge your friends. Play games together, live. And unlock some new dance moves ;)

Join the party – available now on Snapchat inside the Chat bar!

To learn more about Snap Games, visit: snap.com/en-US/news/post/snap-partner-summit-introducing-snap-games
